<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <title>Feedback Form Landing Page</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #4a6bff;
            --secondary-color: #6c757d;
            --accent-color: #00ffcc;
            --text-color: #fff;
            --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e, #0f3460);
            color: var(--text-color);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(74, 107, 255, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: pulse 4s infinite;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, #00ffcc);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease-out;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.3s;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
        }

        main {
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .feature-card i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }

        .feature-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 60px 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.6s;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin: 10px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--accent-color), var(--primary-color));
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .btn:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .btn span {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .social-links a {
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 0.5;
            }
            50% {
                transform: scale(1.1);
                opacity: 0.8;
            }
            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 0.5;
            }
        }

        .feature-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .feature-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        .feature-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Welcome to Our Feedback Platform</h1>
            <p>Your voice matters! Help us create a better experience by sharing your valuable feedback.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="cta-section">
                <h2>Ready to Share Your Thoughts?</h2>
                <div class="actions">
                    <a href="/register" class="btn"><span>Get Started</span></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                    <h3>Real Impact</h3>
                    <p>Your feedback directly influences our improvements and helps us serve you better.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
                    <h3>Easy to Use</h3>
                    <p>Simple and intuitive interface makes providing feedback quick and effortless.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    <h3>Secure & Private</h3>
                    <p>Your responses are confidential and protected with industry-standard security.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
            </div>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Feedback Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>